room_title: Escape room "The Office" by C & C Xscape Rooms in Winona
room_description: You are a spy with many enemies. Your rivals have caught up with you and set a trap for you in an old office building. Almost immediately you find a bomb meant to extinguish you once in for all. You will need to defuse the bomb and make your escape to survive. Only quick thinking and resourcefulness will get you out of this explosive situation!
